flowchart TD
  A[Goal / Work Capsule] --> B[ExperienceKey]
  B --> C[Policy Sampler]
  C --> D[StrategyGenome]
  D --> E[Worker Attempt]
  E --> F[RewardBundle]
  F --> G[FailureMode Classifier]
  G --> H[Positive Pheromone Update]
  G --> I[Negative Pheromone Update]
  G --> J{Mutation Threshold?}
  J -- no --> C
  J -- yes --> K[MutationEvent]
  K --> L[Child StrategyGenome]
  L --> M[Parent-child Tournament]
  M --> N{Decision}
  N -- promote --> O[Child Active]
  N -- suppress --> P[Child Suppressed]
  N -- quarantine --> Q[Child Quarantined]
  N -- keep both --> C
  O --> C
  P --> C
  Q --> R[Audit Only]
